title: 127: Power of Giving Back with Laura Welty
itunes:title: 127: Power of Giving Back with Laura Welty
description:
This interview is with a Highest Self Podcast listener who ended up traveling to Cambodia to visit the Cambodian Childrens Fund after hearing episode 046: Financial Self-Care- Why Abundance Is A Mindset We Need To Pay Attention To. What a true testament that we ALL have so much power to make incredible change in the lives of others.

Sponsor your own Cambodian child or grandmother in need at www.cambodianchildrensfund.org

If you’re ready to give back in a larger way but money is holding you back, join me on my Abundance Mindset Masterclass where we will break through your money blocks that are holding you back from living a life of freedom, purpose and joy. This is a much-requested class after my abundance podcasts and I’m so excited to be teaching you the very lessons that have totally shifted my life. The masterclass includes an interactive live webinar with me and is and just $35.

Join at abundancemindsetmasterclass.com


Intro + Outro Music: Silent Ganges by Maneesh de Moor

Be part of a community that supports you discovering your dharma in Rose Gold Goddesses, the sacred sisterhood collective with community, content, creativity and so much more — learn more about rosegoldgoddesses.com.

Discover Your Dosha (Mind-Body Type) with my free quiz: iamsahararose.com

Connect with me for daily Ayurvedic and modern spiritual wisdom at Instagram: @iamsahararose Facebook.com/iamsahararose Twitter.com/iamsahararose

Order Eat Feel Fresh: A Contemporary Plant-Based Ayurvedic Cookbook and receive my Essential Oils for Your Doshas E-book FREE here: eatfeelfresh.com/book

Join me on book tour in NYC Oct 17 and SD 21 also on the link above!

Join my Awaken Your Powers Masterclass to become a leader in the new paradigm with Shaman Durek: https://www.iamsahararose.com/awaken-your-powers
